---
title: Chimichurri Beef Strip Salad with lemony couscous and cooling cucumber
description: Chimichurri is a vibrant green herby sauce popular in Argentinian, Uruguayan and Chilean cuisine. It's often used as a marinade for meat, making it the perfect dressing for this beef strip salad.
